    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- <u>Welcome to the Planet NESS-444</u> -</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/254cf79ca4853eca5c19d0825ece87e1.poster.avif?t=1758099517\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/254cf79ca4853eca5c19d0825ece87e1.webm?t=1758099517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> The Planet NESS-444 is a vast world full of Adventure, </i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>enemies to face or to have as  allies in battle, </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>valuable resources to gather, mysteries and secrets to unveil.</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Climb the world's highest peaks to discover breathtaking views or </i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>wander into the depths of the planet to reveal ruins of ancient lost civilizations.</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Unique biomes scattered across the land waiting for you to explore them, </i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>until you are able to discover the truth...</i> <br><i>  </i><br><br>  <br><u><strong> </strong></u><strong>- <u>Nessky </u>-<u> </u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/4a5d63a2fff42a92176eb904a2998010.poster.avif?t=1758099517\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/4a5d63a2fff42a92176eb904a2998010.webm?t=1758099517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Nessky are the strange creatures that populate the planet Ness-444.</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>During your adventure you will encounter a wide diversity of creatures, separated into four categories:</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-A minority dwell in shelters, offering you safe places to take refuge and prepare for the difficulties you will encounter.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-The Nessky living in the wild were once friendly...but now</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>corrupted and blinded by darkness you will be seen as a threat....</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Some examples of the strongest species have fallen under the influence of natural gems and have developed powers extremely hard to counter.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Rare species from an adverse past will manifest as calamities, so do not be unprepared.  </i><br><br><i>  </i><br><br><strong>- <u>Combat </u>-</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/d6052f72b90345303bb338484d347ad4.poster.avif?t=1758099517\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/d6052f72b90345303bb338484d347ad4.webm?t=1758099517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Take on powerful enemies using a wide selection of melee weapons : </i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-swords </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-shields </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-axes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-pickaxes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-hammers </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-maces </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-greatswords </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-giant maces</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/ba0f8e0229d7e398545f59bc4da63327.poster.avif?t=1758099517\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/ba0f8e0229d7e398545f59bc4da63327.webm?t=1758099517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Play as Lupio, a nimble creature with hidden powers. You can squeeze into tight spaces and collect special materials.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Gain experience by winning ferocious battles and level up to get new spells, crafting recipes and skill points that will help increase your stats :</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Vitality (HP)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Endurance (Stamina)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Wisdom (Mana)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Strength (Melee Damage)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Agility (Speed/Attack Speed)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Intelligence (Spell Damage)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >+ Crit Chance (% critical hit)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Defeat all the Nessky to discover new materials, weapons and equipment.</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> </i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Find and defeat bosses that carry natural gems to restore the balance of biomes.</i><br><br><i></i><br><br><strong><u>- Nessian Stones -</u></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/04e035de12d96670ac77e0f03debc825.poster.avif?t=1758099517\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/04e035de12d96670ac77e0f03debc825.webm?t=1758099517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Nessian puzzles hide forgotten secrets :</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Enigmatic stones tied to ancient legends.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-They are safe to touch, but figuring out their order is the real test.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-Solve them, and you’ll earn rare items. </i><br><br><i></i><br><br><strong><u>- Crafting -</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/191e580682b825d57de868f34ab33510.poster.avif?t=1758099517\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/191e580682b825d57de868f34ab33510.webm?t=1758099517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Strengthen yourself by forging powerful equipment and accessories that will help you in your adventure.</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Craft Devastating weapons such as swords and shields, broadswords, and giant maces.</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Craft and Find special equipments that can help you reach difficult locations like Highwind Castle or deadly areas like the lands of Toxmoria.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>By leveling up you will gain spells , skill points and new creations recipes for essential items such as potions, food and drink :</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-potions for life, stamina and mana speed and jump boosts. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-foods of increased attack, critical hit and damage</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>-drinks of defense, elemental shields and resistance from Heat/Cold.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/ae076c298cde79d13169b4f723e04f2e.poster.avif?t=1758099517\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297200/extras/ae076c298cde79d13169b4f723e04f2e.webm?t=1758099517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
